pv3199.lib.java.util

Class AbstractStructure<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • pv3199.lib.java.util.AbstractStructure<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - - the type that this data structure will hold.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, DataStructure<E>

    class AbstractStructure<E>
extends Object
implements DataStructure<E>
    A "abstract" implementation of DataStructure. Scope is package-private as the underlying data is simply an ArrayList. This is used for when an abstract data structure is needed rather than, say a LinkedList, to store data and utilize sorting methods from SortMethod.
